[mypy-boto3-builder](https://github.com/youtype/mypy_boto3_builder) carefully generates type annotations for each service, patiently waiting for `boto3` updates. it delivers drop-in type annotations for you and makes sure that: - all available `boto3` services are covered. - each public class and method of every `boto3` service gets valid type annotations extracted from `botocore` schemas. - type annotations include up-to-date documentation. - link to documentation is provided for every method. - code is processed by [black](https://github.com/psf/black) and [isort](https://github.com/pycqa/isort) for readability. ## what's new ### implemented features - fully type annotated `boto3`, `botocore`, `aiobotocore` and `aioboto3` libraries - `mypy`, `pyright`,
